OL,3,CDame Penny Mordaunt 'feared sexual
OL,4,Cviolence' from alleged stalker, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FDame Penny Mordaunt has told a court
OL,8,Fshe "feared sexual violence" from her
OL,9,Falleged stalker.
OL,11,FEdward Brandt, 61, of Freshwater, Isle
OL,12,Fof Wight, is accused of one charge of
OL,13,Fstalking intending serious alarm or
OL,14,Fdistress against the former MP for
OL,15,FPortsmouth North between September 11
OL,16,F2023 and May 12 2024.
