OL,3,CDame Penny Mordaunt 'feared sexual
OL,4,Cviolence' from alleged stalker, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe jury at Southampton Crown Court
OL,8,Fheard that Brandt sent multiple emails
OL,9,Fand phone messages to Dame Penny and
OL,10,Falso turned up at her Portsmouth
OL,11,Foffice out of hours in a bid to meet
OL,12,Fher.
OL,14,FThe trial was told that in her witness
OL,15,Fstatement to police, Dame Penny was
OL,16,Fconcerned that Brandt's references to
OL,17,Fwanting a "personal relationship" with
OL,18,Fher caused her to "fear sexual
OL,19,Fviolence, which is extremely alarming".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
