OL,3,CDame Penny Mordaunt 'feared sexual
OL,4,Cviolence' from alleged stalker, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe told the court: "This comes after
OL,8,Fthe spate of 13 emails plus voice
OL,9,Fmessages, it's after he came to my
OL,10,Foffice out of hours, it's after the
OL,11,Fpolice intervened and our letter of
OL,12,Fcease and desist.
OL,14,F"I believe his motivations for
OL,15,Fpursuing me are not that he wanted to
OL,16,Fhave a conversation about flat tax. I
OL,17,Fdo think they do point to that he is
OL,18,Ftalking about meeting me socially, he
OL,19,Fis not asking for a surgery
OL,20,Fappointment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
