OL,3,CDame Penny Mordaunt 'feared sexual
OL,4,Cviolence' from alleged stalker, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"He wants to meet me after hours, the
OL,8,Fway he is talking about my physical
OL,9,Fappearance and so forth, it's clear
OL,10,Fthat this is not a normal pattern of
OL,11,Fbehaviour."
OL,13,FThe court was told that Brandt was
OL,14,Farrested on March 24 2024 and given a
OL,15,Fconditional caution on April 19 2024,
OL,16,Frequiring him not to contact Dame
OL,17,FPenny. He then left two voicemail
OL,18,Fmessages for her on May 6 and 11.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
