OL,4,Cviolence' from alleged stalker, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe court heard that Brandt made
OL,8,Freference to "wanting to shake her
OL,9,Fhand" around 10 times in his emails,
OL,10,Fincluding one that described her as
OL,11,Fhaving a "gold-plated and precious
OL,12,Fhand".
OL,14,FDame Penny, 52, said that she had
OL,15,Ffound the emails "creepy" but said
OL,16,Fthat "real alarm bells didn't go off
OL,17,Funtil he came to my office".
