OL,3,CDame Penny Mordaunt 'feared sexual
OL,4,Cviolence' from alleged stalker, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FSaying that he referenced her home
OL,8,Faddress in one message, she added: "I
OL,9,Fwas concerned that he knew where I
OL,10,Flived, that he didn't seem to have any
OL,11,Fboundaries and had gone to my place of
OL,12,Fwork out of hours when the office was
OL,13,Fshut."
OL,15,FThe court heard that Dame Penny's
OL,16,Foffice had to increase security
OL,17,Ffollowing Brandt's actions, including
OL,18,Fthe installation of a panic alarm.
