OL,3,CDame Penny Mordaunt 'feared sexual
OL,4,Cviolence' from alleged stalker, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FGemma Freeman, Dame Penny's office
OL,8,Fmanager, said: "She was much more
OL,9,Fwary, more guarded, she was anxious
OL,10,Fabout going out into public spaces
OL,11,Fwhen she was going out to different
OL,12,Fappointments.
OL,14,F"Everything was planned down to the
OL,15,Fnth detail about what could go wrong,
OL,16,Fit was exhausting for her, it was
OL,17,Fexhausting for all of us."
OL,19,FBrandt denies the charge and the trial
OL,20,Fcontinues.
